    "total": "The model extracted the 'Total' value ($77.49) instead of the 'Receipt Total' ($38.75) specified in the gold label.",
    "line_items": "The model failed to extract the 'Mild' item as a separate line item. Instead, it merged it with 'Kickin Sauce' and incorrectly assigned the string 'Mild' to the line_total field."
  }
